43:41.285 --> 43:43.579
God save the queen!

43:43.746 --> 43:45.123
God save the queen!

43:45.289 --> 43:48.126
God save the queen!
God save Papa!

43:48.292 --> 43:50.753
II'

43:50.920 --> 43:52.130
God save Prince Albert!

43:52.296 --> 43:54.382
God save Prince Albert!

43:54.549 --> 43:56.551
God save Prince Albert!

43:56.717 --> 43:59.095
God save Prince Albert!

43:59.262 --> 44:01.180
God save Prince Albert!

44:02.849 --> 44:09.021
II'

44:09.188 --> 44:13.109
Take that, Louis Napoleon!

44:13.276 --> 44:14.610
And that!

44:14.777 --> 44:16.487
Bertie.

44:16.654 --> 44:19.907
<i>Wave something for you.</i>

44:20.074 --> 44:23.202
I don't want
your stupid chocolate!

44:26.998 --> 44:28.166
Bertie?

44:28.332 --> 44:30.209
Bertie!

44:30.376 --> 44:31.460
Ha, ha.

44:31.627 --> 44:33.504
Hey.

44:33.671 --> 44:35.339
What's the matter?

44:35.506 --> 44:37.717
My heart is broken.

44:37.884 --> 44:39.886
Oh, I see.

44:41.762 --> 44:43.055
Well, that's very serious.

44:44.724 --> 44:45.725
But you know,

44:45.892 --> 44:49.312
I think hearts can be mended.

44:52.148 --> 44:53.316
Would you like me to try?

44:55.776 --> 44:57.486
You see, Papa,

44:57.653 --> 45:00.656
I've fallen in love with Heidi.

45:00.823 --> 45:04.869
I think she'd be
a very good queen.

45:05.036 --> 45:08.706
But she says Aunt Feo wants her
to marry Louis Napoleon.

45:11.584 --> 45:13.586
And I love her so much.

45:14.962 --> 45:16.631
Well...

45:17.840 --> 45:19.217
I promise.

45:19.383 --> 45:23.054
You will find
someone else to love.

45:23.221 --> 45:25.431
But I won't be a good king
without her.

45:27.391 --> 45:30.102
Dearest Bertie, trust me.

45:30.269 --> 45:35.775
You will not need Heidi
to be a great king.

45:40.321 --> 45:42.657
Come.

45:42.823 --> 45:47.703
II'

45:55.086 --> 45:57.421
When you said you thought
I should be prime minister,

45:57.588 --> 45:59.548
were you being serious?

45:59.715 --> 46:02.134
Yes, Henry.

46:02.301 --> 46:05.721
I think you've had enough
of foreign affairs.

46:05.888 --> 46:09.100
Does that mean you're going
to be staying in London with me?

46:09.267 --> 46:11.394
How else are you going
to lead the country?

46:22.613 --> 46:23.864
PRESS.

46:24.031 --> 46:26.617
Would you mind?

46:29.370 --> 46:31.747
What on Earth is the matter?

46:31.914 --> 46:33.416
I have just...

46:33.582 --> 46:36.419
discovered that your sister
has been conspiring

46:36.585 --> 46:38.713
with Lord... Pilgerstein

46:38.879 --> 46:41.215
so that her daughter
may marry Louis Napoleon.

46:42.550 --> 46:44.385
Ah.

46:44.552 --> 46:47.680
Well, nothing can come of that
now.

46:47.847 --> 46:48.681
What?

46:48.848 --> 46:50.683
Palmerston has resigned.

46:50.850 --> 46:54.353
Nevertheless...

46:54.520 --> 46:56.605
I trusted her.

46:56.772 --> 46:59.442
I confided in her.

46:59.608 --> 47:03.529
And all the
time, she was deceiving me.

47:04.989 --> 47:10.036
You were right about her,
Victoria.

47:10.202 --> 47:12.496
And I should have
listened to you.

47:16.459 --> 47:19.503
Well, take no satisfaction
in being right-.

47:19.670 --> 47:23.674
Well, would you forgive me if I
did not quite believe you?

47:29.263 --> 47:30.765
Ah.

47:30.931 --> 47:34.226
I wanted to congratulate you
once more.

47:34.393 --> 47:37.480
You must be so proud
that all your hard work

47:37.646 --> 47:40.900
has come to such
a splendid resolution.

47:41.067 --> 47:43.069
Oh.

47:43.235 --> 47:48.491
And thank you, Albert, for
introducing Heidi to Sigmund.

47:48.657 --> 47:49.950
I think She likes him.

47:50.117 --> 47:51.452
And, um...

47:51.619 --> 47:54.372
What do you think
Lord Palmerston would say

47:54.538 --> 47:55.831
if she married him?

47:55.998 --> 47:58.000
Lord Palmerston?

47:58.167 --> 48:00.294
No, you, you no longer care
what he thinks

48:00.461 --> 48:03.089
now that he is not
foreign secretary anymore!

48:05.299 --> 48:08.636
You betrayed me, Feodora.

48:11.972 --> 48:14.934
Oh, Albert.

48:15.101 --> 48:16.352
I'm not so bad, really.

48:18.354 --> 48:20.981
I could have allowed Heidi
to accept your son's proposal.

48:22.733 --> 48:24.360
'Tis a pity-

48:24.527 --> 48:27.947
She would have made
a good queen of England.

48:28.114 --> 48:29.240
As I would have done.

48:30.950 --> 48:32.368
But...

48:32.535 --> 48:38.624
have my standards,
and your unfortunate son...

48:38.791 --> 48:39.875
dues nut meet them.

48:40.042 --> 48:44.755
II'

48:44.922 --> 48:48.384
We will leave in the morning.

48:55.766 --> 48:57.143
Fee...

48:57.309 --> 48:58.436
Feo, wait.

49:00.729 --> 49:03.023
Bertie is my son.

49:03.190 --> 49:05.443
He's just a child.

49:05.609 --> 49:09.238
He's a little boy with feelings
too big for his body.

49:11.782 --> 49:14.201
I can remember
what that was like.

49:17.580 --> 49:19.290
I think you can, too.

49:22.501 --> 49:26.130
<i>You don't have to go, Fee.</i>

49:26.297 --> 49:30.384
I know you were only trying
to do your best for Heidi.

49:30.551 --> 49:32.279
The way Mama was only 'trying
to doing her best

49:32.303 --> 49:36.348
when she sent you to Langenburg
to get married.

49:36.515 --> 49:40.936
But I was Mama's child, too.

49:41.103 --> 49:45.649
No one ever did
their best for me.

49:45.816 --> 49:48.194
And you have wanted
to punish me?

49:48.360 --> 49:49.904
For that?

49:50.070 --> 49:56.118
II'

50:01.248 --> 50:04.168
I know you think
that I have everything,

50:04.335 --> 50:05.836
and that you have nothing.

50:09.757 --> 50:12.468
But there is one thing
I don't have.

50:16.096 --> 50:18.224
A sister.

50:18.390 --> 50:22.770
II'

50:56.262 --> 50:57.721
Mama.

50:59.598 --> 51:03.060
I dreamt I was lost,
and I couldn't find you.

51:03.227 --> 51:09.191
II'

51:17.283 --> 51:22.621
II'

51:32.715 --> 51:34.275
Are you going to stand here
every night?

51:36.844 --> 51:41.724
I wanted to remember that
I had done... something right.

51:44.768 --> 51:47.062
Albert, you've done so much.

51:49.648 --> 51:51.609
Do you think it'll
make a difference?

51:51.775 --> 51:53.235
I do.

51:54.945 --> 51:56.697
It was a day to live forever.

51:56.864 --> 51:58.532
And I could not have done it
without you.

51:58.699 --> 52:00.367
Oh, nonsense.

52:01.994 --> 52:05.497
I did everything I could
to stop you.

52:05.664 --> 52:07.499
Not when it mattered.

52:11.128 --> 52:13.297
No.

52:24.391 --> 52:25.768
Are you all right?

52:25.934 --> 52:27.603
All right.

52:27.770 --> 52:30.189
Just tired.

52:30.356 --> 52:33.942
