52:43.535 --> 52:46.747
This is where we stood
when you...

52:46.914 --> 52:48.499
Proposed.

52:49.667 --> 52:52.920
You were so nervous.

52:53.087 --> 52:54.380
I was.

52:54.546 --> 52:58.300
It was the biggest decision
